Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE and Cushman & Wakefield are pleased to offer for lease Spec 1A, 4Ten Epping. 4Ten Epping is designed to unlock Melbourne’s booming north. An area experiencing significant population growth and industrial development, coupled with direct access to key transport hubs and infrastructure – progress is happening at a rapid pace. The future is coming to the north and 4Ten Epping is here to build it.

The north’s newest and most anticipated Industrial Estate, 4Ten Epping is proudly developed by Frasers Property Industrial. Speculative Development No.1 takes prime position on Cooper Street and boasts exemplary accessibility with immediate access to the Hume Freeway diamond interchange.

Be part of this leading estate and join other major occupiers like Mazda Australia, Crusader Caravans and Intel Engineering who are already upgrading their businesses to 4Ten Epping.

Key Features:
+ Cooper Street exposure
+ Office/Warehouse: 16,972 sqm*
+ Architecturally Designed Office (Mezzanine): 425 sqm*
+ Supercanopy: 2,370 sqm*
+ Heavy Duty Paving: 4,300 sqm*
+ 4 recessed docks
+ 5 on-grade roller doors
+ High clearance warehousing up to 11.5 m offering great volumetric capacity
+ ESFR Sprinkler System
+ 7 tonne post load fibre reinforced concrete slab
+ Targeted 5 star Design and As Built rating under the Green Building Council of Australia (GBCA) Green Star rating tool

*Approx.

Contact the listed agents for further details.

CBRE is pleased to exclusively offer for lease, 348 Cooper Street, Epping. 

Located in Epping’s Cooper Street precinct, the high-quality distribution centre provides flexible sizing options for prospective occupiers, whilst being in direct proximity to major arterial networks and amenity including Hume Freeway/Cooper Street diamond Interchange, Sydney Road, Edgars Road and Pacific Epping Shopping Centre. 

Key Property Details Include:
+ Flexible warehouse areas from 3,000sqm* to 10,200sqm*
+ Comprehensive Development Zone 2
+ 13 recessed loading docks
+ 7 on-grade roller doors
+ ESFR Sprinklers
+ Three street frontages including entry and exit access from both Cooper Street and Taryn Drive

Key Location Proximity Highlights:
+ Hume Freeway: 700 metres*
+ Edgars Road: 580 metres*
+ Melbourne Wholesale Fruit & Veg Market: 400 metres*
+ Pacific Epping Shopping Centre: 1.5km*
+ Epping Railway Station: 2.7km*

Please contact the leasing agents from CBRE for further information on the property.

*approx.

Common.Strapline.Common.Text: FUNCTIONAL OFFICE/WAREHOUSE WITH FLEXIBLE AREAS AVAILABLE

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to offer 24 Jersey Drive, Epping for lease, available now.

This brand-new corporate office/warehouse of 5,346sqm* offers two levels of offices, a high-clearance warehouse with multiple container height roller doors and exceptional loading capabilities.

The property is located only moments from Cooper Street, Hume Freeway, the Hume Highway and M80 Ring Road.

Property features include:
+ Total building area: 5,346sqm*
+ Office area: 582sqm*
+ Warehouse Area: 4,764sqm
+ Sixty-Six (66) car spaces on-site
+ Exceptional loading capabilities allowing for all weather loading/unloading
+ Multiple Container height roller doors
+ Three (3) Phase Power
+ Surplus land to the rear (access via Ricky Way) of 7,172sqm* is also available in addition to the facility 
   should expansion or yard area be required for your operation. 

For further details on this property or your commercial property needs, please contact CBRE 

*approx.

CBRE is pleased to exclusively present 1&2/15 Constance Court, Epping, for lease.

These brand new 710sqm* office/warehouses offer the growing business a new corporate looking facility and encapsulate modern design. 

Due for completion in March 2021, this rare offering in the Connect North Business Park each feature a generous 530sqm* of open clear span warehousing and two levels of office space which will suit your business nicely.

The properties are located within the highly sought-after Connect North Business Park, just off Ohearns Road in Epping. Oherns Road will soon enjoy connection onto the new Hume Freeway diamond interchange providing exceptional access to major road arterials in Melbourne's north.

Property features include:
+ Two office/warehouses each 710sqm*
+ Office areas: 150sqm*
+ Warehouse area: 530sqm*
+ Mezzanine storage areas
+ Kitchen & tearoom
+ Split system heating & cooling
+ Three phase power
+ Nine (9) car spaces
+ Shower
+ Connect North Business Park

For further information on this property or your commercial property needs, please contact Jake George on 0421 221 019

*approx.
